<%= render :partial => 'layouts/opportunities' %>

<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="content-container">

    <div class="main-content">
      <h2 class="mtn">Share a Reflection</h2>
      <p>A reflection is your recap on the state of this opportunity after action was taken.  Were things improved?  Was the action successful?  Would you recommend doing it again?  Etcâ€¦</p>
     <form action="post">
        <fieldset class="form-group top-align">
          <div class="form-block">
            <label for="conversation_title">Title:</label>
            <input class="textbox" id="conversation_title" name="conversation[title]" size="30" type="text" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-block">
            <label for="conversation_title">Your Reflection:</label>
            <textarea class="short textbox" cols="40" id="contribution_content" name="contribution[content]" rows="20"></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-block">
            <input class="submit" id="contribution_submit" name="commit" type="submit" value="Publish" /> &nbsp; or
            <a href="#" id="cancel-contribution">Cancel</a>
          </div>
        </fieldset>
      </form>

    </div><!-- /.main-content -->

    <div class='aside supplementary'>
      <%= render :partial => '/shared/opportunity/participated_actions_selector', :locals => {} %>
      <div class="mod">
        <p><strong>You participated in the following actions, would you like to reference them in your reflection?</strong></p>
        <div class="media inset">
          <input for="petition-check" type="hidden" value="0"><input class="img" checked="" id="person_daily_digest" name="petition-check" type="checkbox" value="1"> <div class="bd"><strong>Petition Cedar Fair to turn Sea World into a whale breeding motel.</strong></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><!-- /.aside -->


  </div>
</div>

